{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"dc78a9ee97e992baf93e32024b3ea7c0ec2aadfe608a35040b841f424cce9f71","slug":"index-2","location":"/pertemuan2/index.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Pertemuan 2 - Memahami Data","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/mfarhancode/pendata","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/mfarhancode/pendata/blob/main/pertemuan2/index.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/mfarhancode/pendata/edit/main/pertemuan2/index.md","thumbnail":"/pendata/build/sepal_length_dist-f640acff3446ed94e3ab770175d9789c.png","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"index.md","url":"/pendata/build/index-6181de20d491b8306e061dbf7f7c6edc.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Referensi: ","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"NZVroJO8Ml"},{"type":"link","url":"https://mulaab.github.io/datamining/memahami-data/","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mulaab - Memahami Data","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"oEtgE1XL7c"}],"urlSource":"https://mulaab.github.io/datamining/memahami-data/","key":"xM1fTmk16s"}],"key":"Qy171j6zFB"},{"type":"thematicBreak","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"RHXHyaCPFq"},{"type":"comment","value":"\n## Macam-macam Data\n\n- **Data Terstruktur** — data dalam bentuk tabel (kolom & baris), mudah disimpan di database/Excel/SQL\n- **Data Tidak Terstruktur** — data yang bervariasi kontennya (email, teks bebas)\n- **Bahasa Alami** — bahasa manusia (Indonesia, Inggris, dll)\n- **Data Machine-Generated** — data otomatis dari mesin (weblog, IoT)\n- **Data Graph** — data keterhubungan antar objek (media sosial)\n- **Data Audio/Video/Citra** — data multimedia\n- **Data Streaming** — data real-time dari ribuan sumber\n\n---\n\n## Tipe Data Atribut\n\n| Tipe | Keterangan | Contoh |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Nominal** | Kategori tanpa urutan | Warna rambut, pekerjaan |\n| **Biner** | Hanya 2 nilai (0/1) | Merokok (ya/tidak) |\n| **Ordinal** | Ada urutan, tapi jarak tidak diketahui | Kecil/Sedang/Besar |\n| **Numerik** | Kuantitatif, terukur | Suhu, berat badan |\n\n---\n","key":"Tn1g5d3Elo"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Implementasi","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"O7p5vsGozs"}],"identifier":"implementasi","label":"Implementasi","html_id":"implementasi","implicit":true,"key":"ZeaMzq8RUM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"link","url":"https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1KIBnoRXwLjL98FPCg7OfFNyJhjZmgLU2?usp=sharing","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Buka di Google Colab","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"DjxQZwzmBt"}],"urlSource":"https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1KIBnoRXwLjL98FPCg7OfFNyJhjZmgLU2?usp=sharing","key":"s2Avqq0dNp"}],"key":"QRO0W6MFc8"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kode Program — Dataset IRIS","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"PoXlYxpnz1"}],"identifier":"kode-program-dataset-iris","label":"Kode Program — Dataset IRIS","html_id":"kode-program-dataset-iris","implicit":true,"key":"A2UPGb6BJf"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Descriptive Statistics","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":